casebody.data:
Emmett F. ANNIS, Appellant, v. FIRST BOND & MORTGAGE COMPANY, Appellee. No. 8357. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 19, 1936. Raphael Dechter, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Smith & Farrar, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed, that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and mandate issued forthwith.
